- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on the task of robots searching for and retrieving objects in unstructured environments. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is also likely as the robot uses an RGBD perception system to locate the target object. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) are also possible categories as the paper discusses algorithmic policies for the robot to perform the task. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is less likely but still possible as the paper involves control policies for the robot's actions.
